external_knowledge:
Overall average closing price refers to the average closing price for each stock symbol across all available data, not limited to the analyses performed by analysts; 
Top stock symbol means the one with the highest average closing price that meets the specified condition; 
Alphabetical order is implied by the ascending order of the stock symbol names.
